snippet.textDisplay:
I have no words actually, There are so many things wrong with this production, or song. Just another perspective.

They have always produced it as Coke Studio India, modifying it to Bharat is still ok as a change.
Maithili Thakur has gone places as an artist, and is also very talented, but this song just wont do justice to her immense knowledge of range she has.
The most heart wrenching part for me was the amazing Sarod players, were no where mentioned in the Title, they both are way more experienced in the industry and way more talented than the Rappers(nothing against Seedhe Maut at all), or Ravi Kishan coming in with that non tone in the end. 
It is just a modern(mash up) song, with fancy beats, fancy stage setting, fancy art direction, which will become a good song for Holi.
The mixing of the beats, too weird, where the vocals should have been higher, it has been covered up by the beats. 
One of the non great songs created by Coke Studio honestly.
